The app was downloaded by 48 pilgrims from 13 countries (Table 1
). Of them, 85% (41/48) completed the first phase (pre-Hajj questionnaire) and of those, 61% (25/41) completed all three study phases (Fig. 2
). Of the 41 participants who completed the pre-Hajj questionnaire, 28 (68.3%) opened the app in Saudi Arabia at least once while having Internet connection.
